 and disease","start":54.24,"end":60.66},{"text":"brokenness and strife Heartbreak","start":61.58,"end":65.38},{"text":"pain pain in the enemy Trying hard to steal your life","start":65.98,"end":70.96},{"text":"But greater is the one with me than anything I''ll face Turn","start":71.56,"end":78.9},{"text":"to Jesus now He knows you''re worth my name Na na na","start":78.9,"end":88.06},{"text":"Lord He sees you and He loves you He came to rescue","start":88.06,"end":94.32},{"text":"you He came to rescue you Take hold of His hand His","start":94.32,"end":99.36},{"text":"promises are true You''re not alone He walks with you Through the","start":99.36,"end":105.7},{"text":"fire He will carry you So lift your eyes again His Word","start":105.7,"end":112.2},{"text":"will lead you through","start":112.2,"end":116.72},{"text":"The arrows of the evil one are real and they can pierce","start":118.44,"end":124.4},{"text":"But put on the armor of God and you will stand up","start":125.32,"end":131.0},{"text":"fierce","start":131.0,"end":131.56},{"text":"When the weight of night surrounds you and hope feels far away","start":132.26,"end":138.88},{"text":"Call upon the name of Jesus He will make a way","start":138.88,"end":150.16},{"text":"You''re not alone","start":154.81,"end":156.92},{"text":"He sees you and He loves you He came to rescue you","start":157.68,"end":162.74},{"text":"He came to rescue you Take hold of His hand His promises","start":162.74,"end":167.68},{"text":"are true You''re not alone He walks with you Through the fire","start":167.68,"end":174.38},{"text":"He will carry you So lift your eyes again His Word will","start":174.56,"end":181.4},{"text":"lead you through Confess and believe He will lift you up","start":181.4,"end":194.18},{"text":"He will lead you through He will lift you up He will","start":194.96,"end":200.34},{"text":"lift you up Turn to Jesus now He will lift you up","start":200.34,"end":204.98},{"text":"He will lift you up He will lift you up"