r away Call upon the name of Jesus, He will make a way You''re not alone, He sees you, and He loves you He came to rescue you, He came to rescue you Take hold of His hand, His promises are true You''re not alone, He walks with you Through the fire, He will carry you So lift your eyes again, His Word will lead you through Confess and believe, He will lift you up He will lead you through He will lift you up, He will lift you up Turn to Jesus now, He will lift you up He will lift you up, He will lift you up Turn to Jesus now, He will lift you up Turn to Jesus now, He will lift you up He will lift you up, He will lift you up You''re not alone, He sees you, and He loves you He came to rescue you, He came to rescue you Take hold of His hand, His promises are true You''re not alone, He walks with you Through the fire, He will carry you So lift your eyes again, His Word will lead you through You''re not less than, you''re more than Because He is greater than anything this world can do to you"}', transcript_state = 'ready', updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE slug = 'not-less-than';

