"be","start":309.86,"end":310.42},{"word":"with","start":310.42,"end":311.54},{"word":"me","start":311.54,"end":313.14}],"lines":[{"text":"I begin another day with quiet hands and tired eyes Needing grace","start":11.58,"end":21.12},{"text":"and mercy new before the sun begins to rise I trust the","start":21.12,"end":27.54},{"text":"road I cannot see is held together by your love So before","start":27.54,"end":34.46},{"text":"I take one step I lift my heart to you above If","start":34.46,"end":40.96},{"text":"the world is loud around me be the whisper I still hear","start":40.96,"end":47.0},{"text":"If my faith feels small and fragile","start":47.0,"end":50.28},{"text":"pull me close and keep me near Please be with me my","start":50.6,"end":58.4},{"text":"Jesus be with me","start":58.4,"end":63.1},{"text":"When the darkness comes when the morning breaks on me Please be","start":63.6,"end":76.1},{"text":"with me my Savior stay with me","start":76.1,"end":83.52},{"text":"My heart needs you my soul needs you","start":84.08,"end":91.08},{"text":"Every breath in me please be with me","start":91.8,"end":100.08},{"text":"Whatever waits for me today you promised you would walk me through","start":103.04,"end":109.54},{"text":"Every trial every turn I will place my hope in you","start":109.54,"end":115.38},{"text":"Teach my hands to move in love teach my feet to follow","start":115.82,"end":121.42},{"text":"peace In the little things I do let my restless striving cease","start":121.42,"end":129.46},{"text":"When I''m standing in the fire when I''m resting in the light","start":129.46,"end":136.4},{"text":"Be the song inside my spirit","start":136.4,"end":139.56},{"text":"be my courage through the night Please be with me","start":140.1,"end":146.26},{"text":"my Jesus be with me","start":146.94,"end":152.18},{"text":"When the darkness comes when the morning breaks on me Please be","start":153.18,"end":165.42},{"text":"with me my Savior","start":165.42,"end":168.82},{"text":"stay with me","start":169.22,"end":172.18},{"text":"My heart needs you","start":172.76,"end":176.18},{"text":"my soul needs you Every breath in me please be with me","start":176.68,"end":188.44},{"text":"Thank you","start":189.1,"end":189.56},{"text":"Lord for all you''ve done Thank you for the work unseen Thank","start":189.9,"end":196.22},{"text":"you for the doors you''ve opened and the places you have carried","start":196.22,"end":201.34},{"text":"me Thank you","start":201.34,"end":203.26},{"text":"Lord for what you''re doing Thank you for the days to come","start":203.66,"end":208.6},{"text":"If I have you I have hope enough","start":208.6,"end":211.94},{"text":"You are still my only one","start":212.32,"end":216.6},{"text":"When the shadows fall please be with me","start":217.32,"end":225.56},{"text":"When the light returns","start":227.44,"end":229.94},{"text":"please be with me Every second","start":231.18,"end":237.24},{"text":"every day keep my heart inside your grace Please be with me","start":237.64,"end":247.54},{"text":"my Jesus be with me","start":247.54,"end":253.32},{"text":"When the darkness comes","start":254.14,"end":257.78},{"text":"when the morning breaks on me Please be with me my Savior","start":258.38,"end":270.46},{"text":"stay with me My heart needs you my soul needs you You","start":270.46,"end":282.78},{"text":"are everything please be with me","start":282.78,"end":291.26},{"text":"Please be with me","start":293.24,"end":298.6},{"text":"softly be with me","start":299.14,"end":302.54},{"text":"At the start of every day please be with me","start":303.08,"end":313.14}],"duration":313.14,"plain_text":"I begin another day with quiet hands and tired eyes Needing grace and mercy new before the sun begins to rise I trust the road I cannot see is held together by your love So before I take one step, I lift my heart to you above If the world is loud around me, be the whisper I still hear If my faith feels small and fragile, pull me close and keep me near Please be with me, my Jesus, be with me When the darkness comes, when the morning breaks on me Please be with me, my Savior, stay with me My heart needs you, my soul needs you Every breath in me, please be with me Whatever waits for me today, you promised you would walk me through Every trial, every turn, I will place my hope in you Teach my hands to move in love, teach my feet to follow peace In the little things I do, let my restless striving cease When I''m standing in the fire, when I''m resting in the light Be the song inside my spirit, be my courage through the night Please be with me, my Jesus, be with me When the darkness comes, when the morning breaks on me Please be with me, my Savior, stay with me My heart needs you, my soul needs you Every breath in me, please be with me Thank you, Lord, for all you''ve done Thank you for the work unseen Thank you for the doors you''ve opened and the places you have carried me Thank you, Lord, for what you''re doing Thank you for the days to come If I have you, I have hope enough You are still my only one When the shadows fall, please be with me When the light returns, please be with me Every second, every day, keep my heart inside your grace Please be with me, my Jesus, be with me When the darkness comes, when the morning breaks on me Please be with me, my Savior, stay with me My heart needs you, my soul needs you You are everything, please be with me Please be with me, softly be with me At the start of every day, please be with me"}', transcript_state = 'ready', updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE slug = 'please-be-with-me';

