2.16},{"word":"wall","start":282.16,"end":282.7},{"word":"won''t","start":282.7,"end":283.2},{"word":"hold","start":283.2,"end":284.08},{"word":"for","start":284.08,"end":284.52},{"word":"long","start":284.52,"end":286.94}],"lines":[{"text":"One more step one more round","start":0.0,"end":8.16},{"text":"when God says move","start":10.3,"end":13.6},{"text":"the walls come down yeah","start":15.28,"end":20.76},{"text":"Hey","start":34.02,"end":35.0},{"text":"There''s an old story still burning about the walls of Jericho","start":42.08,"end":47.74},{"text":"standing tall like they would never","start":48.38,"end":50.88},{"text":"ever let the people through But the people kept on walking even","start":51.92,"end":57.34},{"text":"when it made no sense","start":57.34,"end":59.48},{"text":"God was riding something bigger on the other side of it","start":59.9,"end":64.74},{"text":"His ways are higher","start":65.06,"end":66.64},{"text":"His plans are sure","start":67.8,"end":69.7},{"text":"when He says keep moving","start":70.52,"end":72.86},{"text":"you can trust Him more So blow your horn let the trumpet","start":73.38,"end":79.96},{"text":"sound","start":79.96,"end":81.0},{"text":"if you''re staring at a wall","start":81.48,"end":84.82},{"text":"it''s coming down","start":85.14,"end":86.86},{"text":"God leads the way","start":87.58,"end":89.42},{"text":"so keep marching on","start":90.2,"end":92.5},{"text":"if faith is all you''ve got then blow your horn","start":93.7,"end":97.82},{"text":"There were voices full of laughter","start":98.76,"end":101.82},{"text":"there were doubters on the side","start":102.46,"end":104.7},{"text":"but the ones who chose to follow","start":105.28,"end":107.74},{"text":"knew the Lord would still provide Step by step and lap by","start":108.12,"end":112.86},{"text":"lap","start":112.86,"end":113.22},{"text":"they believed what He had said","start":113.78,"end":116.2},{"text":"and the sound of trust and worship shook the ground beneath their","start":116.58,"end":121.24},{"text":"feet His ways are higher His plans are sure","start":121.24,"end":126.28},{"text":"when He says keep moving","start":127.28,"end":129.56},{"text":"you can trust Him more","start":130.08,"end":132.4},{"text":"So blow your horn","start":133.08,"end":134.8},{"text":"let the trumpet sound","start":135.74,"end":137.46},{"text":"if you''re staring at a wall it''s coming down","start":139.22,"end":143.28},{"text":"God leads the way so keep marching on if faith is all","start":144.28,"end":152.06},{"text":"you''ve got","start":152.06,"end":152.72},{"text":"then blow your horn","start":153.06,"end":155.26},{"text":"What lap are you on right now","start":157.14,"end":159.6},{"text":"What race have you not run","start":159.96,"end":162.1},{"text":"What is standing in your pathway telling you that you are done","start":162.78,"end":167.84},{"text":"Don''t give up in the waiting don''t grow weary in the fight","start":167.84,"end":173.54},{"text":"God is standing with His children and He''s calling you to rise","start":173.86,"end":180.44},{"text":"Don''t stop now stay the course","start":181.48,"end":185.82},{"text":"He is with you","start":187.06,"end":190.66},{"text":"Blow your horn","start":192.48,"end":194.24},{"text":"Tell that wall you''re coming down tell that fear it''s breaking now","start":198.0,"end":203.92},{"text":"tell that doubt you''ve lost your ground","start":204.42,"end":206.68},{"text":"Blow your horn let it ring out","start":207.3,"end":209.66},{"text":"tell that wall I''ve got a song","start":209.96,"end":212.32},{"text":"tell that wall my God is strong Tell that wall you won''t","start":212.98,"end":217.24},{"text":"last long blow your horn keep marching on So blow your horn","start":217.24,"end":222.52},{"text":"let the trumpet sound","start":222.92,"end":225.38},{"text":"if you''re staring at a wall it''s coming down","start":225.8,"end":231.2},{"text":"God leads the way so keep marching on if faith is all","start":232.09,"end":239.96},{"text":"you''ve got","start":239.96,"end":240.6},{"text":"then blow your horn","start":241.16,"end":242.5},{"text":"So blow your horn this is your moment now God is making","start":243.8,"end":250.94},{"text":"every broken strong or bold","start":250.94,"end":253.86},{"text":"He leads the way so keep holding on your victory may be","start":254.54,"end":263.16},{"text":"one more step","start":263.16,"end":264.34},{"text":"So blow your horn","start":265.36,"end":267.94},{"text":"blow your horn","start":268.78,"end":271.48},{"text":"blow your horn","start":272.24,"end":273.84},{"text":"keep marching on","start":274.3,"end":277.5},{"text":"blow your horn","start":278.0,"end":279.42},{"text":"The wall won''t hold for long","start":281.08,"end":286.94}],"duration":286.94,"plain_text":"One more step, one more round, when God says move, the walls come down, yeah. Hey! There''s an old story still burning about the walls of Jericho, standing tall like they would never, ever let the people through. But the people kept on walking, even when it made no sense, God was riding something bigger, on the other side of it. His ways are higher, His plans are sure, when He says keep moving, you can trust Him more. So blow your horn, let the trumpet sound, if you''re staring at a wall, it''s coming down. God leads the way, so keep marching on, if faith is all you''ve got, then blow your horn. There were voices full of laughter, there were doubters on the side, but the ones who chose to follow, knew the Lord would still provide. Step by step and lap by lap, they believed what He had said, and the sound of trust and worship shook the ground beneath their feet. His ways are higher, His plans are sure, when He says keep moving, you can trust Him more. So blow your horn, let the trumpet sound, if you''re staring at a wall, it''s coming down. God leads the way, so keep marching on, if faith is all you''ve got, then blow your horn. What lap are you on right now? What race have you not run? What is standing in your pathway, telling you that you are done? Don''t give up in the waiting, don''t grow weary in the fight, God is standing with His children and He''s calling you to rise. Don''t stop now, stay the course, He is with you. Blow your horn. Tell that wall you''re coming down, tell that fear it''s breaking now, tell that doubt you''ve lost your ground. Blow your horn, let it ring out, tell that wall I''ve got a song, tell that wall my God is strong. Tell that wall you won''t last long, blow your horn, keep marching on. So blow your horn, let the trumpet sound, if you''re staring at a wall, it''s coming down. God leads the way, so keep marching on, if faith is all you''ve got, then blow your horn. So blow your horn, this is your moment now, God is making every broken strong or bold. He leads the way, so keep holding on, your victory may be one more step. So blow your horn, blow your horn, blow your horn, keep marching on, blow your horn. The wall won''t hold for long."}', transcript_state = 'ready', updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE slug = 'so-blow-your-horn';

