a blur, days turn to years like dust on the road, and somewhere in the giving I forgot what I was owed, I play second fiddle to a song I never chose, kept the peace for everybody while I disappeared slow, but there''s a fire in the mirror and it''s calling me by name, saying girl you didn''t lose it, you were buried in the flame, so I''m grabbing my own oxygen mask, I''m done coming last, I gave you my future now I''m taking it back, Today''s my birthday, no more living life your way, I got dreams, I got plans, I got thunder in these hands, Today''s my birthday, watch me turn the page, I ain''t asking for permission, I''m stepping on the stage, raise them up, let the whole room say, Today''s my birthday, I watered everybody''s garden while mine went dry, made a home out of excuses, told myself I was fine, pleasing everyone at my own expense, owe my life for a story that nobody ever read, so grab a chair, take a seat, watch these dreams unfold, that little brass ring shining and I''m reaching for the gold, forget settling, forget playing small, the woman that you counted on ain''t your shadow anymore, I''m done with the silence, done paying the cost, done calling it love when it only leaves me lost, Today''s my birthday, no more living life your way, I got dreams, I got plans, I got thunder in these hands, Today''s my birthday, watch me turn the page, I ain''t asking for permission, I''m stepping on the stage, raise them up, let the whole room say, Today''s my birthday, Today''s my birthday, I''m done doing things your way, Backstabbers, joy killers, soul crushers, dream stealers, manipulators, smooth-talking schemers, two-faced liars, relentless cheaters, This is your exit, there''s the door, I don''t need your chains on my heart anymore, this is my spotlight, this is my name, my light''s coming on, I''m breaking out of that cage, I ain''t bitter, I''m awake, I ain''t broken, I just changed all that time you tried to take, turned to thunder when I walked away, Today''s my birthday, no more living life your way, I got dreams, I got plans, I got thunder in these hands, Today''s my birthday, watch me turn the page, I ain''t asking for permission, I''m stepping on the stage, Today''s my birthday, I''m done wearing old shame, I''m not whispering my story, I''m not shrinking from my name, raise them up, let the whole room say, Today''s my birthday, no more doing things your way, I made a wish, and I made it mine, Today''s my birthday, and it''s my time,"}', transcript_state = 'ready', updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE slug = 'todays-my-birthday';

